'Report Problem', 'সমস্যা জানান'),\n                onPressed: _openReportProblem,\n                child: const Icon(Icons.report_problem_outlined),\n              )\n            : FloatingActionButton.extended(\n                elevation: 2,\n                backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF1F7A5A),\n                foregroundColor: Colors.white,\n                shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(\n                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(18),\n                ),\n                onPressed: _openReportProblem,\n                icon: const Icon(Icons.report_problem_outlined),\n                label: Text(\n                  tr('Report Problem', 'সমস্যা জানান'),\n                  style: TextStyle(letterSpacing: 0.2),\n                ),\n              ),\n      ),\n      bottomNavigationBar: _buildBottomTabBar(\n        context,\n        selectedIndex: _index,\n        onSelected: (value) => setState(() => _index = value),\n      ),\n    );\n  }\n}\n\nclass HomeScreen extends StatefulWidget {\n  const HomeScreen({super.key});\n\n  @override\n  State<HomeScreen> createState() => _HomeScreenState();\n}\n\nclass _HomeScreenState extends State<HomeScreen> {\n  Future<void> _refreshHomeData() async {\n    final data = DataService.instance;\n    try {\n      await Future.wait([\n        data.villageOverview().first,\n        data.donations(limit: 8).first,\n        data.problems(limit: 8).first,\n        data.projects(limit: 8).first,\n      ]).timeout(const Duration(seconds: 8));\n    } catch (_) {\n      if (!mounted) {\n        return;\n      }\n      ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(\n        SnackBar(\n          content: Text(\n            tr(\n              'Refresh completed with limited updates.',\n              'রিফ্রেশ সম্পন্ন হয়েছে, তবে কিছু আপডেট সীমিত ছিল।',\n            ),\n          ),\n        ),\n      );\n    }\n    if (mounted) {\n      setState(() {});\n    }\n  }\n\n  @override\n  Widget build(BuildContext context) {\n    final data = DataService.instance;\n\n    return StreamBuilder<VillageOverview>(\n      stream: data.villageOverview(),\n      builder: (context, overviewSnap) {\n        if (overviewSnap.hasError) {\n          return Center(\n            child: Text(\n              '${tr('Failed to load overview', 'ওভারভিউ লোড করা যায়নি')}: ${overviewSnap.error}',\n            ),\n          );\n        }\n        final loadingOverview =\n            overviewSnap.connectionState == ConnectionState.waiting;\n        final overview =\n            overviewSnap.data ??\n            const VillageOverview(\n              name: 'Our Village',\n              totalCitizens: 0,\n              totalFundCollected: 0,\n              totalSpent: 0,\n            );\n\n        return RefreshIndicator(\n          onRefresh: _refreshHomeData,\n          color: const Color(0xFF1F7A5A),\n          child: ListView(\n            physics: const AlwaysScrollableScrollPhysics(\n              parent: BouncingScrollPhysics(),\n            ),\n            padding: _pagePadding(context),\n            children: [\n              AnimatedEntry(\n                delay: const Duration(milliseconds: 40),\n                offset: const Offset(0, 0.03),\n                child: _HomeHero(\n                  overview: overview,\n                  loading: loadingOverview,\n                  onFundTap: () {\n                    Navigator.of(context).push(\n                      MaterialPageRoute(\n                        builder: (_) => const VillageFundScreen(showDonate: false),\n                      ),\n                    );\n                  },\n                ),\n              ),\n              _vGap(context, 14, 10),\n              AnimatedEntry(\n                delay: const Duration(milliseconds: 110),\n                offset: const Offset(0, 0.03),\n                child: _HomeQuickActions(\n                  onDonateTap: () async {\n                    final canProceed = await _ensureLogin(context);\n                 